desc_short	-----								A 3D Virtual Tabletop that focuses on Miniatures based gaming. Create your own Maps, Quests, Conversations, Items, Miniatures, Stores, Loot Drop Lists. Play your modules or campaigns with up to 10 people as if you were playing around a real table top, using any rule system you like.							
developer									Dragom								
